Name: STARTMOVE
About the game: You and your friend return to his home in the city, which after the nuclear war and the appearance of the 'Goro' mutants will no longer be the same 'home'. You will survive and fight with creatures that become more dangerous each new level. But you need to go through this to collect local riches! STARTMOVE IS: Realistic graphics, cut scenes, atmospheric sound design Several missions - 1 hour of game time with various elements of the gameplay You will be able to drive the car and survive with the first person view during the game Loadout - person/weapon modification (10 models of weapons in the game) This is The Indie game Wave-Shooter with elements of stealth, search, survival horror and its own story
